 "html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">I made this lamb curry for Corné Krige. And he was so impressed with it that he asked me for the recipe. So then I decided to share it with you too.</p>\n\n\n<div data-recipe-slot=\"1\"></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1695\" src=\"/media/uploads/2020/08/Lamskerrie.jpg\" alt class=\"wp-image-6027\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2020/08/Lamskerrie.jpg 2048w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Lamskerrie-600x497.jpg 600w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Lamskerrie-300x248.jpg 300w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Lamskerrie-1024x848.jpg 1024w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Lamskerrie-768x636.jpg 768w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Lamskerrie-1536x1271.jpg 1536w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Lamskerrie-750x621.jpg 750w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Lamskerrie-380x315.jpg 380w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Lamskerrie-760x629.jpg 760w, /media/uploads/2020/08/Lamskerrie-800x662.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\"></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"></p>",
